  "body": "```\r\nProviderError: Error: Transaction reverted and Hardhat couldn't infer the reason. Please report this to help us improve Hardhat.\r\n    at HttpProvider.request (/Users/user/project/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/core/providers/http.ts:49:19)\r\n    at GanacheGasMultiplierProvider.request (/Users/user/project/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/core/providers/gas-providers.ts:312:34)\r\n    at processTicksAndRejections (node:internal/process/task_queues:96:5)\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis occurs when specifying the gas limit:\r\n```js\r\nconst factory = await ethers.getContractFactory(\"MyContract\");\r\nconst contract = await factory.attach(ADDRESS);\r\nawait contract.connect(accounts[0]).func(...args, { gasLimit: 760000 });\r\n```",
